###=======스터디 참여 포인트 적립 API=========
### 1) 성공
POST {{host}}/api/points/study-participation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "studyRoomId": 12,
  "participatedMinutes": 35
}

### 2) 400 - 30분 미만
POST {{host}}/api/points/study-participation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "studyRoomId": 12,
  "participatedMinutes": 20
}

### 3) 409 - 같은 스터디룸 중복 지급 (1번 성공 후 다시 호출)
POST {{host}}/api/points/study-participation
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "studyRoomId": 12,
  "participatedMinutes": 40
}

###=======공부시간 포인트 적립 API=========

### 1) 공부시간 포인트 적립 성공
POST {{host}}/api/points/study-time
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "studyHours": 10
}

### 2) 400 Bad Request - studyHours 누락
POST {{host}}/api/points/study-time
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
}

### 3) 400 Bad Request - studyHours가 0 이하
POST {{host}}/api/points/study-time
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "studyHours": 0
}

### 4) 409 Conflict - 오늘 이미 적립한 경우 (같은 토큰으로 1번 성공 후 다시 호출)
POST {{host}}/api/points/study-time
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "studyHours": 2
}

###=======투두 완료 포인트 적립 API=========

### 1) 성공 (1P 적립)
POST {{host}}/api/points/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "todoId": 1
}

### 2) 409 - 같은 todoId로 중복 지급
POST {{host}}/api/points/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "todoId": 1
}

### 3) 404 - 존재하지 않는 todoId
POST {{host}}/api/points/todos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "todoId": 999999
}

